<h2>Baseline Unit (<code>--lh</code>)</h2>
<p>The <code>--lh</code> token equals <code>1.5rem</code> (one body line-height). Use it for vertical rhythm in prose contexts where spacing should align to the text baseline grid:</p>

<code-block language="css" label="Vertical rhythm with --lh">{{ lhTokenExample | escape }}</code-block>

<h2>Blockquote Hanging Punctuation</h2>
<p>Blockquotes apply <code>hanging-punctuation: first last</code> so that opening and closing quotation marks hang into the margin. This is a progressive enhancement supported in Safari.</p>

